    <releaseNotes>
      • Added new operations for Buffer, Suggest and SingleInputCustomGeocode (findAddressCandidates).
      • Added GetCenter and GetExtent methods to IGeometry.
      • Added Wkt to SpatialReference, setting this sets the other SR properties to null.
      • Added UpdateGeometries extension method for updating geometries but preserving the attributes for a collection of features.
      • Fix to DescribeSite when no folders are present.
    </releaseNotes>
